data.description: Welcome to 843 Trigood Drive! This charming house is now available for sale, offering the perfect blend of comfort and functionality.   On the upper level, you'll find four bedrooms. This layout provides privacy and convenience. With two car garage, parking will never be an issue! Additionally, the bi-level design maximizes space utilization throughout. Step outside onto the backyard covered patio, where you can unwind while enjoying a cup of coffee or hosting delightful gatherings-the space offers,endless possibilities.  This property offers proximity to schools, parks, and shopping centers.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a home that checks all the boxes. Call Christine Chromy at (307) 259-3309 to schedule your private tour and make this home yours today!
